---
title: Veggie Beanie Pie with Garlicky Feta Green Beans
description: We love a good Veggie Pie with Feta Green Beans and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/veggie-beanie-pie-e7171fb6-c46ded2a.jpg
